<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107 0%, #fd7e14 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 30px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #ffc107; color: #212529; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; }
        .security-info { background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
        .warning { background: #f8d7da; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .expiry { background: #d1ecf1; border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üîë Password Reset Request</h1>
            <p>Hi <%= firstName %>, we received a request to reset your password</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
            <p>A password reset was requested for your account: <strong><%= username %></strong></p>
            
            <p>Click the button below to reset your password:</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" class="button">Reset Password</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="expiry">
                <h3>‚è∞ Important Timing Information</h3>
                <p><strong>Request Time:</strong> <%= requestTime %></p>
                <p><strong>Link Expires:</strong> <%= expiryTime %></p>
                <p><strong>Valid For:</strong> 15 minutes from request time</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-info">
                <h3>üîç Request Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= location %></p>
                <p><strong>Device:</strong> <%= device %></p>
                <p><strong>Platform:</strong> <%= platform %></p>
                <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> <%= ip %></p>
                <p><strong>Timezone:</strong> <%= timezone %></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning">
                <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice</h3>
                <p><strong>If you didn't request this password reset:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Ignore this email - your password won't be changed</li>
                    <li>Consider changing your password as a precaution</li>
                    <li>Contact support if you're concerned: <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <h3>üõ°Ô∏è Security Tips</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Choose a strong password with at least 8 characters</li>
                <li>Include uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols</li>
                <li>Don't reuse passwords from other accounts</li>
                <li>Consider using a password manager</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>Note:</strong> If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <p style="word-break: break-all; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; font-family: monospace;"><%= resetUrl %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This password reset link will expire in 15 minutes for security reasons.</p>
            <p>If you didn't request this reset, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Social Media Blog Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>